gs":{"css_class":"","title":"The Circufiber Difference","first_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Circufiber_Icons_white_Clinically_Proven-sized2.png","icon_title_first":"Clinically Proven","icon_para_first":"<p>Clinically proven in a study at Yale School of Medicine to increase circulation in the feet and ankles of people living with diabetes.<\/p>","plus_sign":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/plus-sign.png","second_icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Sock-Design.png","icon_title_Second":"Consumer Verified","icon_para_Second":"<p>In a Quality of Life study of people living with diabetes, 85% of the subjects noticed improvements in their foot\/leg problems within the first 2 weeks of wearing the socks.<\/p>"}},"109368d0-258b-46c7-9e89-825de9baf44e":{"type":"advanced-sock","settings":{"css_class":"","title":"<p>Meet the World's Most Scientifically <\/p><p>Advanced Diabetic  Sock<\/p>","desktop_img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2-weeks-landing-page-2-Recovered.png","mob_img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/infographic_for_mobile-sized.jpg"}},"7d6f253d-8a1e-4a91-8ad9-bb802c82201d":{"type":"customer-reviews","settings":{"css_class":""}},"9dcf7800-4df3-4514-ad65-1bc81769b7df":{"type":"top-health-experts","settings":{"css_class":"","main_heading":"Recommended by Top Health Experts","testi_first_name":"<p><strong>Dr. Adam Mayerson<\/strong><br\/><em>MD, Yale New Haven Hospital, Yale School of Medicine<\/em><\/p>","testi_img_first":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Dr._Adam_Mayerson.jpg","firstdocdetails":"<p>Dr. Mayerson currently serves as the Associate Chief of Medicine at Yale New Haven Hospital and as an Associate Professor at Yale School of Medicine.<br\/><a href=\"\/pages\/scientific-advisory-board\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Scientific Advisory Board\">Read More...<\/a><\/p>","testi_second_name":"<p><strong>Erin Kelly<br\/><\/strong><em>M.Ed, RN, BSN, CDCES, Joslin Diabetes Center<\/em><\/p>","testi_img_second":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Erin_Kelly.jpg","seconddocdetails":"<p>Ms. Kelly currently serves as Clinical Manager of Educational Services at Joslin Diabetes Center and is an accomplished Registered Nurse and Certified Diabetes Care and Education Specialist.<br\/><a href=\"\/pages\/scientific-advisory-board\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Scientific Advisory Board\">Read More...<\/a><\/p>","testi_third_name":"<p>Dr. Matthew Capozzi<br\/><em>DPM, FACFAS, CWS<\/em><\/p>","testi_img_third":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Dr._Matthew_Capozzi.jpg","thirddocdetails":"<p>Dr. Capozzi is a board-certified foot surgeon through the American Board of Foot and Ankle Surgery.<br\/><a href=\"\/pages\/scientific-advisory-board\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Scientific Advisory Board\"><strong>Read More...<\/strong><\/a><\/p>","first_img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/transparent-apma.png","first_textpara":"<p>The American Podiatric Medical Association (APMA) is the leading authority on foot health, and their Seal of Acceptance is a coveted recognition for products that promote foot health. Circufiber diabetic socks have passed the rigorous review process, ensuring their therapeutic and health benefits for diabetics.<\/p>","second_img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/USFDA_2x_b228d3e9-4131-4930-af1d-3f85e0e021ef.png","second_textpara":"<p>The United States Food and Drug Administration (FDA) has determined that Circufiber® products powered by Circulight® IR technology are general wellness medical devices as defined in section 201(h) of the Federal Food, Drug and Cosmetic Act and are general wellness products.<\/p>"}},"906ea7fd-bf8c-408b-9150-66d72fb7a71b":{"type":"try-risk-free","settings":{"css_class":"","risk_img":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Circufiber_Challenge_logo_white_-_sized.png","head_title":"Try Us Risk Free","icon_image_1":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Pain_Reduction_copy_3x_6d798336-714d-4d36-b75b-a512de3ca433.png","icon_head1":"Free Shipping","icon_subhead1":"<p>On all orders over $100.<\/p>","icon_image_2":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Pain_Reduction_copy_3_3x_14fbca57-df49-4155-bb64-81bf2